des: Luxe Life with Candice Bar is all about showcasing the celebrity/entrepreneurs REAL life journey. The ups and downs, the blood, sweat, tears (sometimes literally) and the successes along the way. What it REALLY takes to get to the guests "Luxe Life" and what it takes to continue growing. The show is to inspire, encourage and empower through a real, uncensored honesty conversation. We have the pleasure of empowering millions of listeners/viewers all over the world.
